Dialogs.Dialog: It can't be helped, so I guess I'll feed you.
Do you want me to feed you？
Do you want to be spoiled by Rinko？
Is it not like a couple？
In fact, I've been longing for something like this.
Make it the one you like, Rinko.
Which one you choose is important.
Can you feed it to Rinko？
Just make sure you don't spill it before you eat it.
I can't believe I'm being fed by you. .... hehe.
Are you going to feed me？ .... Okay..
Hehe. I think I'm a little happy...
Yes, if you could just open your mouth？
It takes skill to feed others.
Don't keep me waiting, it's pretty embarrassing.
Do you have a habit of chewing only on one side？
You don't have to look at me when we eat.
Ah, Your mouth... it's on it...
Oh, no. Your mouth is dirty.
Oh！ Did you do that to your mouth？
I would have been happy to take it for you.
I can't believe I'm being fed by you....
What are you going to feed me？
I want to eat delicious foods.
You should feed it to Rinko, too.
Eh, I want to eat that！
Umm.. I want you to feed me...
I'm a little worried about the appearance.
The waiting part makes me the most nervous.
Are you pretending not to hear？
I can do it. I can do it.
I could get addicted to it.♪
Do you not want to continue？
We can feed each other again with this, okay？
You might smile when you remember it later.
You're flirting with me, aren't you？
We are a loving couple, no matter how you look at it.
Ha. .... These are the moments of happiness..
This kind of thing... It's good.
Feels like a couples event... I think it's good. ♪
Ah, ▲小早川＊▲ will eat too？ Here.
